Team Aira

Aira is built by a multidisciplinary founding team combining technology, artificial intelligence, and business strategy, with a shared background in Computer Science and Engineering.

Mehedi Hasan Hridoy

Role: Technology Lead
Background: Computer Science & Engineering (Graduate)
Institution: Daffodil International University

Mehedi leads the overall technical architecture and system design of Aira. He is responsible for building scalable, production-ready systems and ensuring seamless integration across frontend, backend, and infrastructure.

Mahir Dewan Safwan

Role: AI & Machine Learning Lead
Background: Computer Science & Engineering (Undergraduate – Ongoing)
Institution: Rajshahi University of Engineering & Technology (RUET)

Mahir focuses on artificial intelligence and machine learning development for Aira. He works on model integration, intelligent agent behavior, and AI-driven system capabilities.

Imtiaz Bin Alam

Role: Business & Strategy Lead
Background: Computer Science & Engineering (Undergraduate – Ongoing)
Institution: American International University–Bangladesh (AIUB)

Imtiaz leads business strategy, market analysis, and go-to-market planning. He bridges technical innovation with commercial viability, customer needs, and long-term growth strategy.

About Team Aira (Voice-Agent Response)

Team Aira is a collaborative founding team with a strong background in Computer Science and Engineering, bringing together expertise in technology, artificial intelligence, and business strategy. Mehedi Hasan Hridoy, a CSE graduate from Daffodil International University, contributes to system architecture and overall technical development. Mahir Dewan Safwan, a CSE student from Rajshahi University of Engineering and Technology, works on AI and machine learning to build Aira’s intelligent, agentic capabilities. Imtiaz Bin Alam, a CSE student from American International University–Bangladesh, focuses on business strategy, market understanding, and go-to-market planning. Together, the team works as equal contributors, combining engineering depth, AI innovation, and business thinking to build Aira as a voice-native, agentic AI platform.

Aira is the future of next-generation voice agents, designed to be personalized, role-based, and deeply integrated into business workflows. With a focus on seamless user experience and intelligent automation, Aira aims to revolutionize how businesses interact with their customers and manage their operations through voice technology.